<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 14:07:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列国防军袭击黎巴嫩造成七人死亡后，以色列人在以色列北部发射的重型火箭弹中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-killed-in-rocket-barrage-fired-at-northern-israel-after-idf-strikes-in-lebanon/0000018e-7eed-d9f5-a7ae-7eedc2f60000</link><description>来自以色列北部德鲁兹村庄的扎赫尔·比沙拉 (Zaher Bishara) 在真主党向什莫纳镇发射约 30 枚火箭弹后在一栋工业建筑中身亡。此次袭击是对以色列对黎巴嫩发动袭击的报复，该袭击造成七人死亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 13:47:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-killed-in-rocket-barrage-fired-at-northern-israel-after-idf-strikes-in-lebanon/0000018e-7eed-d9f5-a7ae-7eedc2f60000</guid></item><item><title>解释：谁是犹太极端正统派亲巴勒斯坦活动家 Neturei Karta</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/explained-who-are-neturei-karta-the-jewish-ultra-orthodox-pro-palestinian-activists/0000018e-7039-df85-afde-f77d40640000</link><description>在网上和街头，这些激烈反犹太复国主义的极端正统犹太活动分子对他们完全回归《托拉法》的独裁目标以及对哈马斯、伊朗和真主党的拥抱保持沉默。目前，他们的“停止加沙迫害”信息在美国进步示威活动中受到热烈欢迎</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 13:18:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/explained-who-are-neturei-karta-the-jewish-ultra-orthodox-pro-palestinian-activists/0000018e-7039-df85-afde-f77d40640000</guid></item><item><title>我们以色列母亲必须从我们的领导人手中拯救我们的孩子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-27/ty-article-opinion/.premium/we-israeli-mothers-must-save-our-children-from-our-leaders/0000018e-7581-d637-abbf-f7895a6d0000</link><description>我已经被有一天在另一场战争中失去我的儿子的恐惧所压倒，而这场战争是我们具有弥赛亚思想的政府搞砸的，他们更喜欢神奇的思考而不是建设一个可行的未来。现在比以往任何时候都更加紧迫：我们以色列人民必须将他们驱逐出去</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 12:54:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-27/ty-article-opinion/.premium/we-israeli-mothers-must-save-our-children-from-our-leaders/0000018e-7581-d637-abbf-f7895a6d0000</guid></item><item><title>三名巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸被以色列军队杀害，其中两人是在空袭中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/three-palestinians-killed-by-israeli-army-in-west-bank-two-of-them-in-airstrike/0000018e-7f52-d680-a1cf-ff57e8d30000</link><description>以色列国防军宣布，周三，两名武装男子在杰宁的一次空袭中成为目标并被杀，另一名男子向士兵投掷爆炸装置后被射杀</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 10:40:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/three-palestinians-killed-by-israeli-army-in-west-bank-two-of-them-in-airstrike/0000018e-7f52-d680-a1cf-ff57e8d30000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡与正统派的不正当联盟是他的又一失败之举</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-crooked-alliance-with-the-haredim-is-another-feather-of-failure-in-his-cap/0000018e-7cd8-d9f5-a7ae-7edd2ae00000</link><description>以色列总理对军队征召极端正统派人士的法律处理不当，包括拖延、投降和对形势的错误解读。照常。然而，这一次，他的犯罪同伙将首先受苦</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 04:00:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-crooked-alliance-with-the-haredim-is-another-feather-of-failure-in-his-cap/0000018e-7cd8-d9f5-a7ae-7edd2ae00000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡对唯一关心以色列利益的世界强国的令人困惑的蔑视</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-confounding-contempt-for-the-only-world-power-with-israels-interest-at-heart/0000018e-7c90-d680-a1cf-fe97200e0000</link><description>以色列完全依赖美国，但总理 — — 没有美国的批准，他什么也做不了 — — 却喋喋不休地谈论“全面胜利”。此外，美国对以色列的任何额外制裁都会对北方可能发生的战争产生影响</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 04:00:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-confounding-contempt-for-the-only-world-power-with-israels-interest-at-heart/0000018e-7c90-d680-a1cf-fe97200e0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡：我派以色列代表团到美国不是为了“向哈马斯传达信息”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article-live/israeli-hostage-uriel-baruch-was-killed-on-oct-7-body-held-by-hamas-in-gaza-family-says/0000018e-7dc0-d680-a1cf-ffc7736c0000</link><description>约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦当局报告，以色列国防军在杰宁的行动中有 3 人死亡 ■ 加兰特称加沙不会由哈马斯或以色列统治，需要当地替代方案 ■ 以色列南部靠近加沙边境的警报响起 ■ 人质乌里尔·巴鲁克于 10 月 7 日被杀，尸体家人称，哈马斯在加沙控制了</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 02:37:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article-live/israeli-hostage-uriel-baruch-was-killed-on-oct-7-body-held-by-hamas-in-gaza-family-says/0000018e-7dc0-d680-a1cf-ffc7736c0000</guid></item><item><title>长期担任 AIPAC 主席的霍华德·科尔 (Howard Kohr) 将于 2024 年底辞职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/howard-kohr-longtime-aipac-chief-to-step-down-at-the-end-of-2024/0000018e-7cc8-d3d0-a7af-fecaf01c0000</link><description>该公告发布之际，AIPAC 在 2024 年选举周期中的作用和信息传递受到越来越多的审查，特别是在哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击和随后的加沙战争之后</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 22:13:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/howard-kohr-longtime-aipac-chief-to-step-down-at-the-end-of-2024/0000018e-7cc8-d3d0-a7af-fecaf01c0000</guid></item><item><title>美国反驳内塔尼亚胡关于联合国投票损害停火协议的说法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/u-s-rejects-netanyahus-suggestion-that-hamas-rejected-truce-deal-because-of-un-vote/0000018e-7c90-d8a5-addf-7cb328250000</link><description>美国国务院称以色列总理的言论“对人质及其家人不公平”，部分原因是哈马斯在联合国安理会投票前准备了回应</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 22:01:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/u-s-rejects-netanyahus-suggestion-that-hamas-rejected-truce-deal-because-of-un-vote/0000018e-7c90-d8a5-addf-7cb328250000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质乌里尔·巴鲁克 (Uriel Baruch) 家人称，他被认为被绑架，但已于 10 月 7 日被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/hostage-uriel-baruch-was-killed-on-oct-7-body-held-by-hamas-in-gaza-family-says/0000018e-7ca1-d9f5-a7ae-7eade0880000</link><description>35岁的巴鲁克在诺瓦音乐节上被绑架。他留下了妻子 Racheli、两个分别为 8 岁和 5 岁的孩子、父母和三个兄弟。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 21:30:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/hostage-uriel-baruch-was-killed-on-oct-7-body-held-by-hamas-in-gaza-family-says/0000018e-7ca1-d9f5-a7ae-7eade0880000</guid></item><item><title>美国试图澄清以色列遵守拜登国际法要求的情况</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/u-s-attempts-to-clarify-status-of-israels-compliance-with-bidens-demands-on-intl-law/0000018e-7c68-d8a5-addf-7cfbd6f90000</link><description>在美国周一表示尚未发现以色列违反国际法后，美国国务院澄清说，尚未就以色列在加沙使用美国提供的武器时是否遵守美国或国际法做出“最终决定”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 20:50:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/u-s-attempts-to-clarify-status-of-israels-compliance-with-bidens-demands-on-intl-law/0000018e-7c68-d8a5-addf-7cfbd6f90000</guid></item><item><title>品牌形象，但色彩不佳：为什么特朗普将哈马斯袭击归咎于以色列，却忽视了人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-26/ty-article/.highlight/on-brand-off-color-why-trump-blames-israel-for-the-hamas-attack-and-ignores-the-hostages/0000018e-7b8d-d680-a1cf-ff8f94fe0000</link><description>特朗普甚至没有承认人质的身份，因为他们的家人越来越公开地依赖拜登政府来达成协议，同时对内塔尼亚胡未能优先释放他们表示遗憾</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 19:26:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-26/ty-article/.highlight/on-brand-off-color-why-trump-blames-israel-for-the-hamas-attack-and-ignores-the-hostages/0000018e-7b8d-d680-a1cf-ff8f94fe0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对黎巴嫩发动自战争爆发以来最深入的打击；火箭弹向以色列国防军基地发射</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-strikes-northern-lebanon-rockets-fired-towards-idf-base/0000018e-7bc8-d8a5-addf-7bfb90340000</link><description>以色列国防军宣布袭击了黎巴嫩北部真主党空军的一个军事设施，以回应真主党对梅龙山以色列国防军基地的袭击，这是战争爆发以来的第四次袭击</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 18:24:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-strikes-northern-lebanon-rockets-fired-towards-idf-base/0000018e-7bc8-d8a5-addf-7bfb90340000</guid></item><item><title>获释的以色列人质向《纽约时报》讲述了哈马斯被囚禁期间的性虐待经历</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/freed-israeli-hostage-recounts-sexual-abuse-in-hamas-captivity-to-nyt/0000018e-7bd7-d8a5-addf-7bf7afb90000</link><description>阿米特·苏珊娜 (Amit Sousanna) 是第一位讨论绑架者手中性暴力的获释人质，她表示，她分享自己的遭遇是为了提高人们对其余人质被关押条件的认识</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 18:03:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/freed-israeli-hostage-recounts-sexual-abuse-in-hamas-captivity-to-nyt/0000018e-7bd7-d8a5-addf-7bf7afb90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军用复仇诗来鼓舞加沙士兵的士气</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/send-fire-on-gaza-israels-army-uses-revenge-poetry-to-encourage-its-soldiers/0000018e-7bad-d96c-af9f-7fed4ee60000</link><description>以色列国防军出版的选集包含表达复仇欲望的诗歌，并将加沙的战斗描绘成一场宗教战争</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 17:53:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/send-fire-on-gaza-israels-army-uses-revenge-poetry-to-encourage-its-soldiers/0000018e-7bad-d96c-af9f-7fed4ee60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 172 天：以色列消息人士称，人质释放谈判“并未破裂”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-172-hostage-release-talks-have-not-collapsed-says-israeli-source/0000018e-7bae-d8a5-addf-7bbf6a0c0001</link><description>哈马斯拒绝美国释放人质/停火的提议 ■ 部分以色列代表团仍留在卡塔尔继续谈判 ■ 红新月会：以色列国防军撤离并封锁了汗尤尼斯的阿迈勒医院入口 ■ 联合国人权问题特别报告员：以色列在加沙的行动相当于种族灭绝 ■ 美国高级官员在与国防部长加兰特的会晤中寻求缓解美以紧张局势 ■ 战争结束 172 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 17:44:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-172-hostage-release-talks-have-not-collapsed-says-israeli-source/0000018e-7bae-d8a5-addf-7bbf6a0c0001</guid></item><item><title>戈兰高地热门咖啡馆因北部战争永久关门</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/popular-golan-heights-cafe-permanently-closes-doors-due-to-war-in-north/0000018e-7b8a-d8a5-addf-7bbba3460000</link><description>Coffee Anan 是一家位于戈兰高地风景秀丽的本塔尔山的咖啡馆，在以色列国防军宣布以色列北部大部分地区为军事禁区后，该咖啡馆宣布关闭。咖啡馆的名字是前联合国秘书长科菲·安南和希伯来语“云”一词的组合</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 17:38:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/popular-golan-heights-cafe-permanently-closes-doors-due-to-war-in-north/0000018e-7b8a-d8a5-addf-7bbba3460000</guid></item><item><title>数十名以色列军事指挥官警告该法案草案将损害国家安全</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/dozens-of-israeli-military-commanders-warn-draft-bill-would-damage-national-security/0000018e-7b7e-d9f5-a7ae-7f7f972d0000</link><description>在向该国领导人发出的请求中，指挥官们警告不要大幅增加预备役军人服役，同时免除极端正统派人士的计划。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 17:31:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/dozens-of-israeli-military-commanders-warn-draft-bill-would-damage-national-security/0000018e-7b7e-d9f5-a7ae-7f7f972d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列令人不安地否认加沙遭受饥饿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/inside-israels-disturbing-denial-of-starvation-in-gaza/0000018e-7b41-d680-a1cf-ff47b4220000</link><description>以色列当局和亲以色列的键盘侠系统地否认专家研究、援助机构和加沙人自己关于加沙灾难性饥饿的证据，他们有明确的、无耻的动机</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 17:12:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/inside-israels-disturbing-denial-of-starvation-in-gaza/0000018e-7b41-d680-a1cf-ff47b4220000</guid></item><item><title>莫斯科袭击事件后，俄罗斯新的影响力运动试图用草率的希伯来语将责任归咎于西方</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/after-moscow-attack-new-russian-campaign-tries-to-pin-blame-on-west-in-sloppy-hebrew/0000018e-7b63-d96c-af9f-7fe353570000</link><description>莫斯科袭击事件造成至少 139 人死亡，之后以色列社交媒体上出现了数千个账户，并将责任归咎于乌克兰和西方国家。在寻求以色列对恐怖袭击受害者的同情时，该活动的草率希伯来语导致了嘲笑和失败</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 17:05:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/after-moscow-attack-new-russian-campaign-tries-to-pin-blame-on-west-in-sloppy-hebrew/0000018e-7b63-d96c-af9f-7fe353570000</guid></item></channel></rss>